channel.title: Jackz-PVP. V1. [Probably only release]
channel.description:
Well, I'm the owner and hoster of Jackz-PVP earlier named Jackz-Pkz.
Probably only going to release this version.
And, before you say I'm a leecher, I'm not. I've also released this on google forums, Username is :-:Jack:-:.
It has one major feature, which is very helpful. It automatically port forwards for you when starts the server and closes the port when server is closed. This is helpful and very safe (as far as I know of).
Ok, well I'll just post pictures as no one reads lots of writing.. Pictures has made a long writing small:
Client: [IMG]http://i630.photobucket.com/albums/uu25/Jackz-Pkz/untitled5.png[/img]
Home: [IMG]http://i630.photobucket.com/albums/uu25/Jackz-Pkz/untitled.png[/img]
Customs: [IMG]http://i630.photobucket.com/albums/uu25/Jackz-Pkz/untitled4.png[/img]
Edge [IMG]http://i630.photobucket.com/albums/uu25/Jackz-Pkz/untitled3.png[/img]
Teleports [IMG]http://i630.photobucket.com/albums/uu25/Jackz-Pkz/untitled2.png[/img]
Skills Area [IMG]http://i630.photobucket.com/albums/uu25/Jackz-Pkz/untitled1.png[/img]
Credits:
10% Tutorials on Moparscape and google. 50% to the owner of Jad Pk Scape 40% to me as I edited it alot.
Please don't flame, as you wouldn't like it if someone flamed you. Although, please post how I could improve it. Thanks.
I've added the tiniest anti-leech, anyone could fix it.
http://www.mediafire.com/?2kxzinzdzv1 http://www.mediafire.com/?em4olmz2mio
The server file is so large as the port forwarding tools are more than 3mb.
Well, hope you like, enjoy.
